query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('angular5',
'autofac',
'collision-detection',
'drawing',
'field',
'fonts',
'hibernate',
'ipython',
'port',
'redux',
'sbt',
'struts2',
'unity-container',
'web-crawler');
